The best fritura truck I have been at in the Bronx. The food is great and made on the spot. My absolute favorites here are the pig ears (orejitas), bofe (beef lung), and the morcilla (blood sausage) with yuca fries or tostones (always ask for extra mojito/you will thank me later lol). The chicken chimi is the bomb if you are into it. Enjoy/buen provecho!
One of the best spots in NY.

DIAAAACHÉ!!! Que ricura, y siempre listo para satisfacer! Mi favorito siempre es la longaniza con yucca frita, y batata con carnita....un english simple put is...DAAAAYUM!! My favorite is the Dominican sausage (longaniza)  with cassava, also steak and sweet yam...blood sausage (morcia) is great too with tostones fried green plantains.  God bless!
